What is the output of the following code?

const [a, , b] = [10, 20, 30, 40];
console.log(a, b);

In the code below, what does 'this' refer to inside the setTimeout callback?

const obj = {
  name: 'WBB',
  greet() {
    setTimeout(function() {
      console.log(this.name);
    }, 100);
  }
};
obj.greet();

What is the output of this code?

const a = { x: 1, y: 2 };
const b = { y: 3, z: 4 };
const c = { ...a, ...b };
console.log(c);

What does the following generator function produce?

function* gen() {
  yield 1;
  yield 2;
  return 3;
}

const result = [...gen()];

What is the output of the following code?

const obj = { a: 1, b: { c: 2 } };
const copy = { ...obj };
copy.a = 99;
copy.b.c = 99;

console.log(obj.a, obj.b.c);
